Package de.thkoeln.cvogt.android.propanimutil_demos

Demonstrates the functionality and the usage of the package de.thkoeln.cvogt.android.propanim_utilities which provides utility classes for the Android property animation technique.

For details, please watch these three videos: Overview, Code, Demo

and read the documentation of the classes AnimatedGuiObjectCV and AnimationViewCV.


This work is provided by Prof. Dr. Carsten Vogt, Technische Hochschule Köln, Fakultät für Informations-, Medien- und Elektrotechnik, Germany

under GPLv3, the GNU General Public License 3, http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html.
